Steps.Message: Following on from our previous message, we can now confirm we have switched power off to 37 properties. This is to allow our engineers to safely remove trees that are on the overhead lines. If your electricity has gone off, you can keep updated by texting POWER followed by your full postcode to 80876 (e.g. POWER IP3 8AA). Standard text fees apply.

We became aware of this power cut at 20:21. We’re sorry for any disruption this may have caused you. We didn’t know in advance there would be a power cut, but now that we know, our teams will do everything they can to get your power back quickly. Engineers in our control room have switched some customers power back on in your area. To get everyone’s power back on we may need to attend to investigate and make repairs. We’ll continue to update you until everyone’s power is back on.
Steps.Name: We are restoring customers automatically
